addPosition((address,address,uint24),(ui.details: at a highlevel, the function  a) borrows liquidities from uniswap  b) computes and pays premiums for existing position if it exists c) execute the trade with the borrowed funds + margin  d) stores relevant data

forceClose((address,address,uint24),(add.details: filler needs to specify fillerPayAmount under his discretion, ideally it is the minimum amount he has to pay such that the AMM can be made whole, while maximizing his profitwhen the trader's position is closed by this function he will no longer be entitled to his margin and the filler's (max) profit will be his remaining margin param fillerPayAmount denotes the amount the filler is willing to pay for the ENTIRE positiondepending on the uniswap tick he might not get to buy the entire position but only a portion of it, at which the price he will buy the portion is the ratio fillerpayamount/totalPosition

multicall(bytes[]).details: Receives and executes a batch of function calls on this contract.

payPremium((address,address,uint24),bool.details: deducts from the borrower's premium deposit balance, sends funds to the poolManager,

reducePosition((address,address,uint24),.details: two forms of frontrun attacks: 1. Manipulting ticks before this transaction such that the system repays incorrectly this is mitigated via specifying min and max ticks 2. regular swap frontruns this is mitigated by specifying minOutput of the swapWhen current tick is inside borrowed range, can only reduce position using limit orders + fillers

addPosition((address,address,uint24),(ui.notice: add to a positions if a position already exists, or create a new position

depositPremium((address,address,uint24),.notice: deposits premium per position, if isToken0 depositing token1 and viceversa

forceClose((address,address,uint24),(add.notice: when a position can be force closed, system allows filler to close position and collect all remaining proceeds in return

payPremium((address,address,uint24),bool.notice: allows borrower compute premium owed pay it, increase back premium deposit to mindeposit levels, and update repaytime

swapAndDepositPremium((address,address,u.notice: toSwapAmount is amount in position token that needs to be swapped to borrowed token
